Comments can be given on the following draft policies and By-laws: Copies of these draft policies and By-laws are obtainable from the City of Mbombela’s website available from 23 February 2021. Please submit your written comments within a period of 30 days from the date of the advert. The written comments may be sent by email to: thembam@mbombela.gov.za or hand delivered at Office No. Z5, City of Mbombela’s Jones Offices, 7 Jones Street, Mbombela.  For more information or enquiries please contact Mr Themba Mona on  013 759 2325 or email him at thembam@mbombela.gov.za. Visit the City’s website at www.mbombela.gov.za.